{"id":396508,"date":"2020-11-06T11:24:16","date_gmt":"2020-11-06T10:24:16","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/?p=396508"},"modified":"2022-01-11T17:49:42","modified_gmt":"2022-01-11T16:49:42","slug":"ctrader-indicators","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/en\/ctrader-indicators\/","title":{"rendered":"The Top 8 cTrader Indicators that can change your trading for better!"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>cTrader is a very popular trading platform and compared to MetaTrader4, it can offer more advanced tools and much easier user experience. That&#8217;s why we offer cTrader to our FTMO traders as one of the platforms. Besides the classic indicators, you can find some custom indicators on the internet and that&#8217;s exactly what we have tested here. We picked the TOP 8 cTrader Indicators that can change your trading for the better!<\/em><\/p>\n<h1 class=\"title style-scope ytd-video-primary-info-renderer\">MetaTrader4 vs cTrader &#8211; Which one is better?<\/h1>\n<p>Two of the most popular forex trading platforms in the industry, MetaTrader4, and cTrader. What are the pros and cons of each one?<\/p>\n<p>Watch this video and you will find out!<\/p>\n<div class='avia-iframe-wrap'><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Metatrader4 vs cTrader - Which platform is the BEST for Trading Forex | FTMO\" width=\"1500\" height=\"844\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/T3H5i6srACU?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe><\/div>\n<h1>How to Instal cTrader Indicators<\/h1>\n<p>For installing downloaded cTrader indicators, all you have to do is double-click the downloaded file and they will install automatically.<\/p>\n<p>Once you install the indicator, you will find it in the indicator tab on the left side panel.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/indicators.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396521\" src=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/indicators.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1845\" height=\"964\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/indicators.jpg 1845w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/indicators-300x157.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/indicators-1030x538.jpg 1030w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/indicators-768x401.jpg 768w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/indicators-1536x803.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/indicators-1500x784.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/indicators-705x368.jpg 705w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1845px) 100vw, 1845px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2>Hull MA Indicator<\/h2>\n<p>Hull moving average is a very popular indicator used by many traders.<\/p>\n<p>Developed by Allan Hull, HMA offers a very fast and smooth moving average.<\/p>\n<p>It almost completely eliminates lag and improves smoothing at the same time.<\/p>\n<p>Depends on the settings, it offers a great intraday, but also a long-term moving average that helps traders staying in trends as long as possible.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/HMA.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396518\" src=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/HMA.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1848\" height=\"968\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/HMA.jpg 1848w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/HMA-300x157.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/HMA-1030x540.jpg 1030w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/HMA-768x402.jpg 768w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/HMA-1536x805.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/HMA-1500x786.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/HMA-705x369.jpg 705w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1848px) 100vw, 1848px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ctrader.com\/algos\/indicators\/show\/17\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Source<\/a><\/p>\n<h2>Forex Heat Map Panel for cTrader<\/h2>\n<p>Forex heatmap panel tracks 9 currencies and shows strength and weakness against each other.<\/p>\n<p>You can watch those currencies that are extremely strong or weak and look for a potential reversal.<\/p>\n<p>Compared to the classic indicator, you will find the Forex Heat Map panel in the cBot section which is located right below the indicator button on the left panel.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/heatmap.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396527\" src=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/heatmap.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1843\" height=\"973\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/heatmap.jpg 1843w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/heatmap-300x158.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/heatmap-1030x544.jpg 1030w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/heatmap-768x405.jpg 768w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/heatmap-1536x811.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/heatmap-1500x792.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/heatmap-710x375.jpg 710w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/heatmap-705x372.jpg 705w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1843px) 100vw, 1843px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/clickalgo.com\/ctrader-forex-heat-map\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Source<\/a><\/p>\n<h2>Correlation<\/h2>\n<p>Do you know what happens when you long EUR\/USD and short USD\/CHF at the same time?<\/p>\n<p>You are taking the same bet as these two pairs are highly correlated and will most likely move together.<\/p>\n<p>Therefore if you are wrong on one trade, you are most likely wrong on the second one as well which can lead to a much bigger loss than planned.<\/p>\n<p>The correlation indicator allows you to compare two instruments so you will quickly see their historical and current correlation.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/correlation.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396611\" src=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/correlation.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1840\" height=\"955\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/correlation.jpg 1840w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/correlation-300x156.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/correlation-1030x535.jpg 1030w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/correlation-768x399.jpg 768w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/correlation-1536x797.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/correlation-1500x779.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/correlation-705x366.jpg 705w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1840px) 100vw, 1840px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ctrader.com\/algos\/indicators\/show\/465\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Source<\/a><\/p>\n<h2>Larry Williams Indicator Package<\/h2>\n<p>Larry Williams is a professional legendary trader. In 1987, Larry Williams won the <em>World Cup<\/em>\u00a0Championship of Futures Trading from the Robbins Trading Company, where he turned $10,000 to over $1,100,000 (11,300<wbr \/>%).<\/p>\n<p>Throughout his career, he also created several indicators and systems, and you can get all of them in this cTrader indicator package.<\/p>\n<p>For those that are fans of Larry Williams and want to use his methods, this is a must-have.<\/p>\n<p>The package contains:<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>Williams Ultimate Oscillator (custom)<\/li>\n<li>Williams Advance\/Decline Line<\/li>\n<li>Williams Cycle Identifier<\/li>\n<li>Williams VIX FIX<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/ctrader-williams-cycle-identifier.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396542\" src=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/ctrader-williams-cycle-identifier.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"998\" height=\"564\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/ctrader-williams-cycle-identifier.png 998w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/ctrader-williams-cycle-identifier-300x170.png 300w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/ctrader-williams-cycle-identifier-768x434.png 768w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/ctrader-williams-cycle-identifier-705x398.png 705w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 998px) 100vw, 998px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/clickalgo.com\/ctrader-larry-williams-indicators\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Source<\/a><\/p>\n<h2>Candlestick Patterns &#8211; Doji<\/h2>\n<p>This simple indicator points out the Doji candlestick pattern on your chart.<\/p>\n<p>Doji candlestick often signals a potential reversal in the market, therefore you will never miss important market turns!<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/doji.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396545\" src=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/doji.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1842\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/doji.jpg 1842w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/doji-300x156.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/doji-1030x537.jpg 1030w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/doji-768x400.jpg 768w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/doji-1536x801.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/doji-1500x782.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/doji-705x367.jpg 705w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1842px) 100vw, 1842px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ctrader.com\/algos\/indicators\/show\/1628\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Source<\/a><\/p>\n<h2>Tick Volume Indicator<\/h2>\n<p>This indicator converts standard volume into a more accurate tick-based volume histogram that is much better suited for trading Forex.<\/p>\n<p>It highlights low and high climatic volume. This way we can easily spot strong breakouts or exhaustion near the end of a trend.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/tickvol.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396548\" src=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/tickvol.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1842\" height=\"966\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/tickvol.jpg 1842w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/tickvol-300x157.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/tickvol-1030x540.jpg 1030w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/tickvol-768x403.jpg 768w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/tickvol-1536x806.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/tickvol-1500x787.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/tickvol-705x370.jpg 705w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1842px) 100vw, 1842px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ctrader.com\/algos\/indicators\/show\/666\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Source<\/a><\/p>\n<h2>Market Hours<\/h2>\n<p>This simple indicator shows the different trading sessions, London, New York, and Tokyo.<\/p>\n<p>It is fully customizable and you might need to adjust it according to your timezone.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/markethours.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396551\" src=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/markethours.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1841\" height=\"956\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/markethours.jpg 1841w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/markethours-300x156.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/markethours-1030x535.jpg 1030w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/markethours-768x399.jpg 768w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/markethours-1536x798.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/markethours-1500x779.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/markethours-705x366.jpg 705w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1841px) 100vw, 1841px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ctrader.com\/algos\/indicators\/show\/115\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Source<\/a><\/p>\n<h2>USDX Dollar Index<\/h2>\n<p>By default, traders cannot see the dollar index inside their cTrader platform, this indicator fixes that!<\/p>\n<p>It plots the Dollar index as an oscillator running below the chart so you can watch it any time you want.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/dxy.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-396554\" src=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/dxy.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1838\" height=\"953\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/dxy.jpg 1838w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/dxy-300x156.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/dxy-1030x534.jpg 1030w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/dxy-768x398.jpg 768w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/dxy-1536x796.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/dxy-1500x778.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/ftmo.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/dxy-705x366.jpg 705w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1838px) 100vw, 1838px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ctrader.com\/algos\/indicators\/show\/459\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Source<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>cTrader is a very popular trading platform and compared to MetaTrader4, it can offer more advanced tools and much easier user experience. That&#8217;s why we offer cTrader to our FTMO traders as one of the platforms. Besides the classic indicators, you can find some custom indicators on the internet and that&#8217;s exactly what we have [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":44,"featured_media":406654,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":true,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[670],"tags":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/396508"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/44"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=396508"}],"version-history":[{"count":9,"href":"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/396508\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":563008,"href":"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/396508\/revisions\/563008"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/406654"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=396508"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=396508"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/ftmo.com\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=396508"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}